filled “with a lot of her exotic toys and products and lubricants and all of those wonderful things you hopefully might not need,” Parks said. PHOTOS: The Bravo Curse! 10 Reality Stars Who Made All The Wrong Headlines After Appearing On TV Burruss’ bachelorette party will air as a special episode on June 22 in her Bravo spin-off series, Kandi’s Wedding. 
